### =====================================================
### PLACEMENT PORTAL BACKEND DEMO FLOW (PROFESSOR MODE)
### =====================================================
### Use this exact order live.
### If app startup fails, first free port 8080:
###   netstat -ano | findstr :8080
###   taskkill /PID <PID_FROM_ABOVE> /F
### Then run:
###   cd j:\portal\portal
###   .\mvnw.cmd spring-boot:run
### =====================================================

